Cloud: You can learn any one cloud first like AWS, GCP, Azure and much more but you can only grab your full command on one cloud first then you can switch the cloud easily according
to their use case in your industry. I personally recommend you to learn AWS cloud because it will provide you a free tier account for 1 year with minimal services which help us to 
move ahead in your journey of cloud. After that you can switch any cloud in which you want to move forward.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Terraform: Terraform is a infrastructure as a code tool which help us to manage your infrastructure on a cloud which give you to manage your cloud easily in the today's competitive world.
